4. Steps to load unhealth indexes from ECK
  a.	Go to devtools from top menu
  b. type command GET _cat/indices?health=yellow and run
  c. results will display left side
  d. if you should delete them then use below command to delete one by one
  e. DELETE /<index_name>

Vi filebeat.yml
Set enabled:true
Paths: /opt/atlassian/jira/logs/access_log.*
 
Set Reload.enabled: true
Delete Setup.kibana //line
Delete output.elasticsearch //line
 
Uncomment output.logstash;
Uncomment & change the host to hosts: [abc1jdc08.ed.cps.google.com:5044]
(Save the file)
 
•	Start Filebeat service using below command:
 
Service filebeat start
•	To Check logs:

Tail -f /var/ log/filebeat/filebeat
